name: There Will Be End
description:
WARNING !!!
YOU DIDNT FINISH THE GAME WHEN THE MAINMENU THAT SAYS 
THERE WILL BE START!!! CONTINUE THE GAME

There Will Be End is a puzzle and with a hint of a story game 

In it you have to play and finish puzzles with keeping in mind that THE END IS THE start

Game was developed for the Game Zanga Jam

Keys To Press

WASD Or Arrows To Move

E to interact (E is the use key)

And that's it hope you enjoy and Good Luck ^^

Thank you very much.
